paper_abstract: A pair of Mond-Weir type multi-objective higher order symmetric dual programs over arbitrary cones is formulated. Weak, strong and converse duality theorems are established under higher order K-F-convexity assumptions. Our results generalize several known results in the literature. (C) 2010 Elsevier Ltd. All rights reserved.
paper_title: Higher order symmetric duality in nondifferentiable multi-objective programming problems involving generalized cone convex functions
